    symbol has_sink=exists sink:item: is_sink(sink) and close(food_vegetable, sink)
    return has_sink

    body:
        achieve inside(vegetables, sink)
        # Position the vegetables inside the sink

        bind faucet: item where:
            is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet, sink)
        achieve_once is_on(faucet)
